Package it.polito.verifoo.random

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RandomConstraints
    Generates a random set of requirements for a service graph
    RandomGraph
    Generates a random service graph for Verifoo with random requirements and set of policies
    RandomInputGenerator
    Wraps the creation of a completely random input file for Verifoo
    RandomTopology
    Generates a random topology for Verifoo ("Hosts" element and "Connections" element)
